snippet.title: Satan (Part 1)(1/2) - Amstrad CPC
snippet.description:
By Dinamic 1989
Great game as you would think of a Dinamic game. Has 2 parts, so you basicly get 2 games for 1 price. No music, but who will notice that with so great a game. Top class gameplay with lovely graphics and audio. Game has a VERY strickt timelimit so even if the game has a lot of area, you need to take the fastest rute and pick up the hourglasses in time or its game over. Wish Bionic Commando had had just half the quality game that this one has.
